{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867532911,"sessionID":"ses_2860e6a98ffeCYVckYxGnvJ9yT","part":{"id":"prt_d79f1a37a001hqoip3QylMtkvV","messageID":"msg_d79f1965d001DoJggIndJrumBo","sessionID":"ses_2860e6a98ffeCYVckYxGnvJ9yT","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_dbf0a4ba7fa146f5a76e7201","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Find AR-028 archive files","prompt":"Search the workspace at /home/dsj/benchmark for any files related to \"AR-028\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\", \"sdk-python\", or \"agentcube\" archive/change records. Look for:\n1. Any files with \"AR-028\" in the name or content\n2. Any files mentioning \"AgentRuntimeClient\" \n3. Any archive, changelog, or change record files in the workspace\n4. Any SDK-related documentation or spec files\n\nSearch thoroughly using glob patterns like **/*AR-028*, **/*archive*, **/*change*, **/*sdk*, **/*agent*, and grep for content matches.\n\nReturn all relevant file paths and their contents that could help summarize what was completed and what was deferred for this change.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2860e4deeffe7o2VnwYWbYU6uA (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is a comprehensive summary of all findings related to AR-028, AgentRuntimeClient, sdk-python, and agentcube.\n\n---\n\n## Summary: AR-028 -- SDK AgentRuntimeClient\n\n### What is AR-028?\n\nAR-028 is an Architectural Requirement titled **\"SDK AgentRuntimeClient\"** for the AgentCube project. It is a Python SDK change (module: `sdk-python`, language: Python, size: M) that implements a high-level client for invoking Agent Runtime workloads through the AgentCube Router.\n\n---\n\n### All Relevant File Paths\n\n#### 1. AR-028 Change Request Directory (scaffolded, mostly TODO placeholders)\n\n| File | Path | Status |\n|------|------|--------|\n| proposal.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/proposal.md` | Skeleton with TODOs (33 lines) |\n| design.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/design.md` | Skeleton with TODOs (41 lines) |\n| delta-spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md` | **Fully populated** with 228 lines of Gherkin-style scenarios |\n| tasks.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md` | **Fully populated** with 11 tasks (T-1 through T-11), dependency graph, parallelizable groups, and 12 acceptance criteria |\n\n#### 2. SDK Source Code (Implementation -- already complete)\n\n| File | Path | Lines |\n|------|------|-------|\n| AgentRuntimeClient | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | 79 lines |\n| AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | 80 lines |\n| Package init | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/__init__.py` | 4 lines (exports both clients) |\n| Clients init | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | 9 lines |\n| pyproject.toml | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/pyproject.toml` | 19 lines |\n\n#### 3. Test File (newly created during ST-5)\n\n| File | Path | Lines |\n|------|------|-------|\n| test_agent_runtime.py | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/tests/test_agent_runtime.py` | 837 lines, 45 new tests |\n\n#### 4. Base Spec/Design Documents\n\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| python-sdk/design.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/design.md` |\n| python-sdk/spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md` |\n\n#### 5. Benchmark/Registry Files\n\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| report.py (AR registry) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/scripts/report.py` (line 102: AR-028 definition) |\n| sdd_tee_report.json | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/reports/sdd_tee_report.json` (line 315: AR-028 entry) |\n| agentcube_tdd_manifest.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` |\n\n#### 6. Session Log Files (ST-0 through ST-5)\n\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| ST-0 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-028_ST-0.log` |\n| ST-1 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-028_ST-1.log` |\n| ST-2 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-028_ST-2.log` |\n| ST-3 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-028_ST-3.log` |\n| ST-4 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-028_ST-4.log` |\n| ST-5 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-028_ST-5.log` |\n\n---\n\n### What Was Completed\n\n**Core SDK implementation** (already existed, verified complete during ST-4/ST-5):\n- **`AgentRuntimeClient`** (`agent_runtime.py`, 79 lines) -- high-level public client with:\n  - Constructor with args: `agent_name`, `namespace`, `router_url`, `verbose`, `session_id`, `timeout`, `connect_timeout`\n  - `router_url` resolution from argument or `ROUTER_URL` env var (raises `ValueError` if missing)\n  - Session bootstrapping via `dp_client.bootstrap_session_id()` when `session_id` is `None`\n  - Context manager protocol (`__enter__` / `__exit__`)\n  - `invoke(payload, timeout)` -- validates session, calls data plane, returns parsed JSON\n  - `close()` -- delegates to data plane client\n\n- **`AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`** (`agent_runtime_data_plane.py`, 80 lines) -- low-level HTTP client with:\n  - `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` class constant\n  - Base URL construction via `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/{ns}/agent-runtimes/{name}/invocations/\")`\n  - HTTP session with `HTTPAdapter(pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)`\n  - `bootstrap_session_id()` -- GET invocation URL, reads session header, raises `ValueError` if missing\n  - `invoke(session_id, payload, timeout)` -- POST with session header and JSON body, returns raw `requests.Response`\n  - `close()` -- closes HTTP session\n\n- **Public exports** -- `AgentRuntimeClient` exported from `agentcube/__init__.py`, `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` from `agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n\n- **Tests created** (`test_agent_runtime.py`, 837 lines, 45 new tests covering all T-1 through T-10 tasks):\n  - T-1: Base URL construction, session header constant, HTTP adapter pool settings, constructor field storage, default timeouts\n  - T-2: Bootstrap session ID -- returns ID when header present, raises ValueError when missing, raises HTTPError on non-2xx, calls raise_for_status\n  - T-3: Invoke -- correct URL/session header/JSON body, default timeout, explicit timeout, returns raw response, calls raise_for_status\n  - T-4: Close -- closes HTTP session, idempotent\n  - T-5: Client init defaults -- all defaults, explicit args, env var resolution, ValueError when no router_url, dp_client construction\n  - T-6: Session bootstrapping/reuse -- None triggers bootstrap, provided skips bootstrap, verbose DEBUG/INFO levels\n  - T-7: Context manager -- enter returns self, exit calls close, exit with exception re-raises, with-statement normal and exception flow\n  - T-8: Client invoke -- valid session calls dp_invoke and returns parsed JSON, None/empty session raises ValueError, custom timeout, None timeout\n  - T-9: Client close -- delegates to dp_client, idempotent\n  - T-10: Integration tests -- full lifecycle, pre-provisioned session, custom timeout, exception flow, missing router_url, missing header\n\n- **Test results**: 86/86 tests pass (45 new + 41 existing from AR-027)\n- **AR-028 module coverage: 100%** (`agent_runtime.py` + `agent_runtime_data_plane.py`)\n- **All 12 acceptance criteria (AC1-AC12) met**\n\n---\n\n### What Was Deferred / Out of Scope\n\nFrom the delta-spec.md and tasks.md, the following items were **not addressed** in AR-028:\n\n1. **T-11 (Lint/Type-check/Coverage gate)** -- The `ruff check`, `mypy`, and coverage gate tasks were marked as part of T-11 but the ST-5 session log indicates `requires-python` was changed from `>=3.10` to `>=3.9` and one test assertion was fixed (removing `verbose` attribute check), but no full lint/type-check/coverage report was run as part of AR-028 specifically.\n\n2. **Examples and E2E scripts** -- `examples/agent_runtime_usage.py` and `scripts/e2e_picod_test.py` are listed in the base spec as non-library artifacts but were not created.\n\n3. **Async/gRPC support** -- Explicitly out of scope.\n\n4. **CLI integration** -- The `AgentRuntimeClient` is an SDK-only component; no CLI commands were added to use it.\n\n5. **Proposal.md and Design.md in changes/AR-028/** -- These remain as skeleton TODO files. The actual design work was done in the top-level `design.md` (for AR-027, which also covers AR-028) and `python-sdk/design.md`. The delta-spec.md and tasks.md were fully populated, but the proposal.md and design.md in the AR-028 directory were never filled in beyond their templates.\n\n---\n\n### Key Design Details\n\n- **Architecture**: 3-layer design -- Public Client (`AgentRuntimeClient`) -> Data Plane Client (`AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`) -> HTTP Utilities (`create_session`, `get_logger`)\n- **Session bootstrap**: Unlike `CodeInterpreterClient` (AR-027) which uses a control plane to create sessions, `AgentRuntimeClient` bootstraps sessions by sending a GET request to the Router and reading the `x-agentcube-session-id` response header\n- **Dependency**: AR-027 (SDK CodeInterpreterClient) -- shares utilities, exceptions, and package scaffolding\n- **Timeout defaults**: read timeout 120s, connect timeout 5.0s, with per-call override support\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2860e4deeffe7o2VnwYWbYU6uA","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Find AR-028 archive files","time":{"start":1775867376142,"end":1775867532908}}}}
