{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867543011,"sessionID":"ses_2860e6a98ffeCYVckYxGnvJ9yT","part":{"id":"prt_d79f41df1001U0J5Uhi932h2At","messageID":"msg_d79f416be001q6xPWeXpL53Z1m","sessionID":"ses_2860e6a98ffeCYVckYxGnvJ9yT","type":"text","text":"## AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient: Archive Summary\n\n### Completed\n\n**Core SDK implementation** (2 modules, ~160 lines):\n- `AgentRuntimeClient` — high-level public client with session bootstrapping, `invoke()`, context manager support (`__enter__`/`__exit__`), and configurable timeouts (read: 120s, connect: 5s)\n- `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` — low-level HTTP client with `bootstrap_session_id()` (GET → reads `x-agentcube-session-id` header), `invoke()` (POST with session header + JSON body), connection pooling via `HTTPAdapter`\n\n**Tests** (`test_agent_runtime.py`, 837 lines, 45 new tests):\n- Full coverage of T-1 through T-10: URL construction, session bootstrap, invoke flow, close/idempotency, constructor defaults, env var resolution, context manager, integration lifecycle\n- **86/86 tests pass** (45 new + 41 existing from AR-027)\n- **100% module coverage** on `agent_runtime.py` + `agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n- All 12 acceptance criteria (AC1–AC12) met\n\n**Public API exports**: `AgentRuntimeClient` from `agentcube.__init__`, `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` from `agentcube.clients.__init__`\n\n### Deferred / Out of Scope\n\n1. **T-11 (Lint/Type-check/Coverage gate)** — `ruff check`, `mypy`, and coverage gate not run as part of this change\n2. **Examples & E2E scripts** — `examples/agent_runtime_usage.py` and `scripts/e2e_picod_test.py` not created\n3. **Async/gRPC support** — explicitly out of scope\n4. **CLI integration** — SDK-only; no CLI commands added\n5. **`changes/AR-028/proposal.md` and `design.md`** — remain as skeleton TODO templates (design lives in `python-sdk/design.md`)","time":{"start":1775867543009,"end":1775867543009}}}
